                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JANE BATES</hi> (29)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18651218-131-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18651218-131-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
